
Dependencies
============

* JDK 1.5 or greater


Building Pivot (using Ant: http://ant.apache.org/)
==================================================

* To compile all Pivot source files into binary class files:

  $ ant

* To regenerate the JAR files in the lib folder:

  $ ant package

* To generate Javadoc

  $ ant doc

* To generate the Pivot distribution

  $ ant dist
